name: somethings looming
description: This one began as a castle sketch from a thirty day drawing challenge of making a castle and a monster everyday with no references.  Eventually I modeled every castle in Cinema 4D hoping new ideas would spark something for an entire piece.  This one was more of an exploration of the type of landscapes and worlds some of these castles could exist in. (copyright)@davekiehl for personal use only.
